I live here in Houston, Texas. the ISS just flew over my house at the same time the Space Walk was being preformed. I decided to cheer on our astronauts and catch up on my KSP and Orbital Mechanics studies. post your funny spacewalk pictures, pictures related to the International Space Station, or other related things!
